Secondary forte first because I love FBoT and Rain spells. Then getting either pet crits or pet flurry first(may buy both depending on cost) for dps since it will benefit both my solo play and groups. Then Im getting elemental agility. Its better for the pet to completely dodge an incoming attack than simply adding about 90-400hps with elemental durability.
